<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="89800000t" end="125300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}今ならまだ間に合うから</b></font></p>
<p begin="89800000t" end="125300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>现在还来得及</b></font></p>
<p begin="126100000t" end="163200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}撤退した方がいいよ</b></font></p>
<p begin="126100000t" end="163200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>还是撤退掉比较好</b></font></p>
<p begin="163200000t" end="212500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}もっと勘違いしてしまう前に</b></font></p>
<p begin="163200000t" end="212500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>在造成更大的误会之前</b></font></p>
<p begin="214100000t" end="235400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}staple　stable</b></font></p>
<p begin="214100000t" end="235400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>staple　stable</b></font></p>
<p begin="237100000t" end="274200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}君をとじた言葉の針</b></font></p>
<p begin="237100000t" end="274200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>将你缝起来的言语之针</b></font></p>
<p begin="274600000t" end="341800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}いつの間にか　この胸に刺さってしまってた</b></font></p>
<p begin="274600000t" end="341800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>不知不觉刺到了我的胸口</b></font></p>
<p begin="342200000t" end="362200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}痛い</b></font></p>
<p begin="342200000t" end="362200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>好痛</b></font></p>
<p begin="363000000t" end="386000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}君のせいだよ</b></font></p>
<p begin="363000000t" end="386000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>都是你的错</b></font></p>
<p begin="386400000t" end="422200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}来ないで　こんなこんな私を</b></font></p>
<p begin="386400000t" end="422200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>不要靠近这样的我</b></font></p>
<p begin="423100000t" end="459000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}見ないで　そんなそんなとこまで</b></font></p>
<p begin="423100000t" end="459000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>不要看向那样的地方</b></font></p>
<p begin="459400000t" end="496100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}話さないで　あんなあんな笑顔で</b></font></p>
<p begin="459400000t" end="496100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>不要带着如此的笑容来说话</b></font></p>
<p begin="496100000t" end="536500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}どんな誰にも</b></font></p>
<p begin="496100000t" end="536500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>不管对谁</b></font></p>
<p begin="544000000t" end="582400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}どこまででも続く　この空のようね</b></font></p>
<p begin="544000000t" end="582400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>就好像无限延伸的天空一般</b></font></p>
<p begin="582800000t" end="617900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}終わりのない永遠を誓って</b></font></p>
<p begin="582800000t" end="617900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>许下永不终结的永远的誓言</b></font></p>
<p begin="618700000t" end="656200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}いじわるで優しい　その海のようね</b></font></p>
<p begin="618700000t" end="656200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>既坏心眼又温柔  就好像这片大海一样</b></font></p>
<p begin="656600000t" end="692100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}心に飛び込んだら　受け止めて</b></font></p>
<p begin="656600000t" end="692100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>如果扑入心怀的话  请接受吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="692900000t" end="773000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}重さじゃ量れないこんな想い</b></font></p>
<p begin="692900000t" end="773000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>想将这无法用重量来测量的心意</b></font></p>
<p begin="776400000t" end="840600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34"><font face="MS Gothic" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>{\an8}君だけに今伝えるから</b></font></p>
<p begin="776400000t" end="840600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35"><font face="方正黑体_GBK" size="30" color="#cf0402"><b>只传达给你</b></font></p>
<p begin="910700000t" end="950700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33"><b>{\an8}<font size="45">历物语  历与花</font></b></font></p>
<p begin="910700000t" end="950700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="36"><b>{\an8}本字幕仅供交流试看之用，如您喜欢本作品，请支持购买正版。<br />若因私自散布传播造成法律及相关一切问题，华盟字幕社概不负责。</b></font></p>
<p begin="950700000t" end="980700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="36"><b>{\an8}翻译：痛爱的飞鱼；后期：snow。</b></font></p>
<p begin="965700000t" end="980700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">五月</font></p>
<p begin="995700000t" end="1010800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">五月九日</font></p>
<p begin="1020300000t" end="1035800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">周二的傍晚</font></p>
<p begin="1041600000t" end="1091700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我和战场原绯多木走在从那栋废弃私塾大楼回家的路上</font></p>
<p begin="1100400000t" end="1120000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她曾经历尽了痛苦</font></p>
<p begin="1124200000t" end="1155500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">历尽了那些足具让她感到麻木的痛苦</font></p>
<p begin="1163800000t" end="1212600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而就在昨天  她写病魔斗争的日子也终于画上了句号</font></p>
<p begin="1222200000t" end="1261000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">人们常说「大病初愈才知健康的可贵」</font></p>
<p begin="1263500000t" end="1324800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">对于久病我的来说  像这样正常地走路也是件蛮稀奇的事</font></p>
<p begin="1329400000t" end="1347300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哦？是嘛</font></p>
<p begin="1351500000t" end="1377400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an3}那么  今后又该怎么办呢？</font></p>
<p begin="1379900000t" end="1392400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？你指的是什么？</font></p>
<p begin="1398200000t" end="1443300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你看  关于这件事忍野先生不是要对我收取费用吗？</font></p>
<p begin="1449900000t" end="1467500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你平时还存钱吗？</font></p>
<p begin="1473700000t" end="1496200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没有没有  欠钱的事倒是时有发生</font></p>
<p begin="1519600000t" end="1551300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">战场原  你知道什么怪谈吗？</font></p>
<p begin="1579700000t" end="1626000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">忍野他是个以收集怪异谈为本职的专家</font></p>
<p begin="1628900000t" end="1684800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果你知道些什么少见的怪异谈或者稀有的都市传说的话</font></p>
<p begin="1684800000t" end="1715200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说不定可以用这些东西来抵账</font></p>
<p begin="1720200000t" end="1770300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">很不巧  除了我自己亲身经历的怪异谈以外我一概不知</font></p>
<p begin="1789000000t" end="1795300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哦呀？</font></p>
<p begin="1903300000t" end="1911200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你要干嘛？</font></p>
<p begin="1914600000t" end="1918700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？</font></p>
<p begin="1927100000t" end="1941300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不要随便碰我</font></p>
<p begin="1948400000t" end="1959200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  不好意思</font></p>
<p begin="1968400000t" end="2000100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我只是看你突然要往马路上跑</font></p>
<p begin="2003400000t" end="2044700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我不是想往马路上跑  只是想去看一下那个东西</font></p>
<p begin="2048500000t" end="2054700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那个东西？</font></p>
<p begin="2093900000t" end="2126900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">看来这附近出过车祸</font></p>
<p begin="2131000000t" end="2159400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好像是这样  应该是最近发生的吧</font></p>
<p begin="2159400000t" end="2201900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过要是你因为要去看那束花而被车撞了</font></p>
<p begin="2201900000t" end="2222400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那这位死者可就真是没法成佛了</font></p>
<p begin="2222400000t" end="2234100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你倒是注意点啊</font></p>
<p begin="2257000000t" end="2269100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我想起来了</font></p>
<p begin="2271600000t" end="2300800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？想起来了？想起什么了？</font></p>
<p begin="2306200000t" end="2326700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是件很可怕的事情  阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="2330400000t" end="2339200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">到底是啥啊？</font></p>
<p begin="2351300000t" end="2381300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这是本公主的命令  给我办得妥妥当当的</font></p>
<p begin="2398800000t" end="2421300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}谁家公主是像你这样说话的？</font></p>
<p begin="2483500000t" end="2498500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">五月十日</font></p>
<p begin="2501400000t" end="2561100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">奉战场原排多木之命  我爬上了直江津高中教学楼的楼顶</font></p>
<p begin="2568100000t" end="2606100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哦  还真是  真和战场原说的一样</font></p>
<p begin="2610700000t" end="2652400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在禁止入内的楼顶  放着一束新鲜的花</font></p>
<p begin="2709100000t" end="2744200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">楼顶禁止入内  那你是怎么进去的？</font></p>
<p begin="2749600000t" end="2787100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">人家虽然不是羽川姐姐  但咱好歹也是个优等生</font></p>
<p begin="2790900000t" end="2827200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">找下借口向老师借把钥匙还是很容易的</font></p>
<p begin="2830900000t" end="2854700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你去楼顶又是要干嘛？</font></p>
<p begin="2859700000t" end="2909300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我进入直江津高中之后  对于人身安全问题进行了一番考虑</font></p>
<p begin="2916800000t" end="2955600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她是一个对其他人戒备心很强的女生</font></p>
<p begin="2961500000t" end="3001100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">和羽川对直江津高中进行的调查不同</font></p>
<p begin="3001100000t" end="3025700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她是为了分辨哪里危险哪里安全</font></p>
<p begin="3025700000t" end="3065300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">谁是伙伴谁是敌人而进行一番彻底调查</font></p>
<p begin="3071100000t" end="3118300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">于是她便在禁止入内的楼顶看到了那束花</font></p>
<p begin="3124100000t" end="3156600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这和「怪异谈」以及「怪谈」都不太一样</font></p>
<p begin="3163700000t" end="3202100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过仔细想一想  这也是件很不可思议的事情</font></p>
<p begin="3219200000t" end="3242600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  的确是件很不可思议的事情</font></p>
<p begin="3249700000t" end="3318500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因内在直江津高中十八年的历史中  没有发生过一例学生死亡的事件</font></p>
<p begin="3338500000t" end="3348900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="23"><b>{\an8}<font face="方正准圆_GBK"><font size="33">…算了，先不管这个</font></font></b></font></p>
<p begin="3348900000t" end="3358500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="23"><b>{\an8}<font face="方正准圆_GBK"><font size="33">先想想我该怎么回到教学楼里吧…</font></font></b></font></p>
<p begin="3374800000t" end="3391900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那么  你觉得如何？忍野</font></p>
<p begin="3397700000t" end="3435300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我刚才说的那件事值不值十万日元？</font></p>
<p begin="3459900000t" end="3467800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">怎么了？</font></p>
<p begin="3474500000t" end="3526600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木同学  你知道那位小姐的电话或者邮箱地址吗？</font></p>
<p begin="3532000000t" end="3546600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不知道  我没问过</font></p>
<p begin="3551600000t" end="3572500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那你就帮我这么转告她吧</font></p>
<p begin="3578300000t" end="3626300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「抱歉让您失望了  请您再找别的方法支付费用」</font></p>
<p begin="3630900000t" end="3680100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那你能不能先跟我说清楚  为什么这件事一文不值？</font></p>
<p begin="3685100000t" end="3729700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">首先  关于阿良良木同学你们看到的那个车祸现场</font></p>
<p begin="3733500000t" end="3765200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就在上个月  那里有人因车祸身亡</font></p>
<p begin="3768100000t" end="3785200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎  是嘛</font></p>
<p begin="3789400000t" end="3839400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那个地方从结构上来说本来就容易发生车祸</font></p>
<p begin="3856900000t" end="3900300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">的确  战场原她也差点跑到马路上面去</font></p>
<p begin="3905700000t" end="3962900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  不过  战场原似乎是为了去看那束供奉在那里的花束</font></p>
<p begin="3965800000t" end="3990400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">并不算是道路的结构问题</font></p>
<p begin="3996200000t" end="4050500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">问题就在于  从来没有人从教学楼的楼顶跳楼自杀</font></p>
<p begin="4050500000t" end="4085500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或者说  也从来没有发生过坠楼事故</font></p>
<p begin="4085500000t" end="4125500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">却出于某种原因  在所有的教学楼顶都放着花束</font></p>
<p begin="4125500000t" end="4138000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是这样没错吧</font></p>
<p begin="4141000000t" end="4168100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？呃…啊  没错</font></p>
<p begin="4172200000t" end="4205200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">先不说实际上有没有可能会坠楼</font></p>
<p begin="4205200000t" end="4242300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">楼顶的确是个容易发生事故的地方</font></p>
<p begin="4246900000t" end="4266900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">正因为如此才会禁止入内</font></p>
<p begin="4280300000t" end="4344500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  开放楼顶的学校一般都会用高得很离谱的围栏把它围起来</font></p>
<p begin="4348300000t" end="4359100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就是这样</font></p>
<p begin="4362400000t" end="4416700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不论是道路还是学校内  总有一些容易发生事故或事件的地方</font></p>
<p begin="4421200000t" end="4462100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">简单说来  就是能量之源的对立面</font></p>
<p begin="4477500000t" end="4498800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就是灵力不好的地方吗？</font></p>
<p begin="4500900000t" end="4546800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好像的确有类似的地方  比如鬼门方位之类的</font></p>
<p begin="4551000000t" end="4576800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  和那些还是不一样的</font></p>
<p begin="4581400000t" end="4624400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在构造上容易发生事故的地方  在全国到处都有</font></p>
<p begin="4624400000t" end="4669000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">除此之外还有自杀者喜欢选择的自杀场所</font></p>
<p begin="4675700000t" end="4739500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而这些归根结底都是地形或者环境之类的问题  和灵力无关</font></p>
<p begin="4743600000t" end="4797000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">战场原突然往马路上跑也不是因为怪异或者幽灵作祟</font></p>
<p begin="4797000000t" end="4824600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">只是出于观察那束花的视角问题</font></p>
<p begin="4828300000t" end="4894600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  所以我打算过一会儿去改一下那束花的位置</font></p>
<p begin="4908400000t" end="4954700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木同学  如果供奉的花可以招来车祸</font></p>
<p begin="4967200000t" end="4994700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你难道就不觉得相反的情况也有可能发生吗？</font></p>
<p begin="5012300000t" end="5038900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">接下来便是后日谈  或者说这次的结局</font></p>
<p begin="5045600000t" end="5078100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过这次的结局可是发生在很长时间之后</font></p>
<p begin="5085200000t" end="5155700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为我被忍野的那一席话所说服  并没有向战场原报告这件事</font></p>
<p begin="5161100000t" end="5196590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">等我再想起这件事  已经是五月下旬了</font></p>
<p begin="5205800000t" end="5213700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我想起来了</font></p>
<p begin="5226200000t" end="5279200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">简单来说  那些花束是校方对楼顶进行安全管理的一个环节</font></p>
<p begin="5284600000t" end="5299200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">对楼顶进行安全管理？</font></p>
<p begin="5301300000t" end="5338000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  和管理钥匙还有设置围栏是一样的</font></p>
<p begin="5341300000t" end="5403500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过和这两项相比  这更像是一种安慰或者迷信  类似于玄学之类的东西</font></p>
<p begin="5408100000t" end="5441000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在楼顶放一束花  这算是什么安全管理？</font></p>
<p begin="5445600000t" end="5466000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这种做法倒是的确有些讨厌</font></p>
<p begin="5471900000t" end="5514800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在楼顶放一束花  假装得好像有人曾经死在这里</font></p>
<p begin="5518600000t" end="5572800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">反过来以此来提醒人们这里危险  相当于警示标志一样</font></p>
<p begin="5576100000t" end="5617900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">警示标志？就像「前方为事故多发区」之类的？</font></p>
<p begin="5621200000t" end="5672500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可能是考虑到只写上「危险」两个字显得太普通  起不到什么效果</font></p>
<p begin="5677100000t" end="5725500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟「曾经有人死在这里」的信息会给人留下深刻的印象</font></p>
<p begin="5756700000t" end="5789700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过这种效果真的会大于玄学吗？</font></p>
<p begin="5794700000t" end="5847300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这就像是心理安慰一样  有一半是出于好玩  忍野他是这么说的</font></p>
<p begin="5853100000t" end="5897300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为封锁和围栏本来就已经足以防止出现坠楼事故了</font></p>
<p begin="5900600000t" end="5928200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过这也很难说能够做到万全</font></p>
<p begin="5934400000t" end="5976500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟实际上也有像你这样随便说个谎就往楼顶跑的学生</font></p>
<p begin="5981100000t" end="6025300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我说阿良良木同学  能不能不要把别人说得好像骗子一样</font></p>
<p begin="6031200000t" end="6049500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我只是能言善辩而已</font></p>
<p begin="6052000000t" end="6085800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你这叫毒舌好不好  毒舌加上能言善辩简直是糟糕到极点了</font></p>
<p begin="6112500000t" end="6178800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以对于这样难以保证万全的状况  校方便把这种迷信当做心理安慰</font></p>
<p begin="6185100000t" end="6202200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  原来如此</font></p>
<p begin="6208400000t" end="6276000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过忍野先生为什么只听阿良良木同学口述就能如此断定呢？</font></p>
<p begin="6282700000t" end="6304400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这也不算是断定吧</font></p>
<p begin="6306500000t" end="6342700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你看  我和你都想错了一件事</font></p>
<p begin="6346900000t" end="6365300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不管是事故还是自杀</font></p>
<p begin="6369900000t" end="6414100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果真的有人从楼顶坠落  放花束的地方也不应该是在楼顶</font></p>
<p begin="6417000000t" end="6422000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊…</font></p>
<p begin="6428200000t" end="6446200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而应该是在落下的地面</font></p>
<p begin="6472500000t" end="6497900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">原来如此  这一点还真是想错了</font></p>
<p begin="6501200000t" end="6534200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过这应该是所有人都可能会犯的错吧</font></p>
<p begin="6538800000t" end="6555500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}你这自我圆场还真是快</font></p>
<p begin="6563800000t" end="6640500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过对于放花束的人来说  就算明知不合理也只能把花束放在楼顶</font></p>
<p begin="6646400000t" end="6655600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而</font></p>
<p begin="6659700000t" end="6691800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这种行为在今后恐怕就不会再有了</font></p>
<p begin="6700600000t" end="6706400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错</font></p>
<p begin="6711900000t" end="6763200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">楼顶的改造工程便是让我想起这件事的契机</font></p>
<p begin="6769400000t" end="6800700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而学校不得不对楼顶进行改造</font></p>
<p begin="6800700000t" end="6872900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">则是因为有传言说「前一阵有学生沿着教学楼外侧爬上了楼顶」</font></p>
<p begin="6878700000t" end="6913300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">校方恐怕也没想到会有人蠢到从教学楼外侧入侵</font></p>
<p begin="6913300000t" end="6942500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">校方恐怕也没想到会有人蠢到从教学楼外侧入侵</font></p>
<p begin="6951300000t" end="6971300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">设置新围栏的工程费用数目自然不小</font></p>
<p begin="6971300000t" end="7013400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">除此之外  如果被人知道人侵者的身份就是我的话</font></p>
<p begin="7019700000t" end="7044300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我恐怕也不止是退学那么简单</font></p>
<p begin="7051400000t" end="7093500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">当然  怂恿我做这件事的战场原也不可能有好下场</font></p>
<p begin="7103100000t" end="7113500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="7119400000t" end="7130600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我知道</font></p>
<p begin="7134000000t" end="7156500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这件事是只属乎我们两个人的秘密</font></p>
<p begin="7161900000t" end="7191100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  光是「秘密」的话恐怕还有些不够</font></p>
<p begin="7195700000t" end="7216100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不够的话又该怎样？</font></p>
<p begin="7221500000t" end="7246100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">当然就要像之前一样处理咯</font></p>
<p begin="7251600000t" end="7262800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">之前一样？</font></p>
<p begin="7286200000t" end="7297900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">把它忘掉吧</font></p>
<p begin="7525200000t" end="7580600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">将烦恼踢开  石头顺势滚落</font></p>
<p begin="7525200000t" end="7580600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}悩み 蹴飛ばして石が転がってく</font></p>
<p begin="7581100000t" end="7638200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">稍加掩饰的  是四月的事情</font></p>
<p begin="7581100000t" end="7638200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}少し 誤魔化した あれは四月のこと</font></p>
<p begin="7638200000t" end="7692400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">曾经的我们都是好奇心旺盛的开朗孩子</font></p>
<p begin="7638200000t" end="7692400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}好奇心旺盛で 明るい子供でした</font></p>
<p begin="7692800000t" end="7752500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">在背后推着我们的是那一天开始的冒险</font></p>
<p begin="7692800000t" end="7752500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}背中押したのは あの日からの冒險</font></p>
<p begin="7752500000t" end="7809600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">追寻着那些不出格的热度</font></p>
<p begin="7752500000t" end="7809600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}はみ出せない熱を追いに行って</font></p>
<p begin="7810000000t" end="7863800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">到处闲逛</font></p>
<p begin="7810000000t" end="7863800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}道草をしよう</font></p>
<p begin="7882600000t" end="7939800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">将重要的梦想放进箱子</font></p>
<p begin="7882600000t" end="7939800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}箱に乗せ 大切な夢</font></p>
<p begin="7939800000t" end="7996100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">踩起脚踏板  将它带到远方</font></p>
<p begin="7939800000t" end="7996100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}ペダル回し 遠くまで さぁ 持ち出そう</font></p>
<p begin="7996100000t" end="8049900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">传说中我们的未来</font></p>
<p begin="7996100000t" end="8049900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}噂した 僕の未来は</font></p>
<p begin="8050300000t" end="8087000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">有着我们各自的模样</font></p>
<p begin="8050300000t" end="8087000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}個々人の伸びる丈に</font></p>
<p begin="8087000000t" end="8129100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">怎么说也听不懂</font></p>
<p begin="8087000000t" end="8129100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}聞いてもわからない</font></p>
<p begin="8129500000t" end="8189200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">听不懂啊听不懂</font></p>
<p begin="8129500000t" end="8189200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}わからない わからない</font></p>
</div>
